Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.37,0:20:31.88,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HFFAE04&\blur3}It was something nice and sweet ’til I see the real
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.88,0:20:40.39,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HFFAE04&\blur3}It’s been always something cruel, dark and sore
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.39,0:20:45.02,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HACD837&\blur3}Chikazuku dabi kirameku tabi
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.02,0:20:49.06,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HACD837&\blur3}Konomune oshiyoseru
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.06,0:20:53.04,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HDB2594&\blur3}Ureshii demo kurushii
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.04,0:20:57.40,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HDB2594&\blur3}Koko kara saki wa muri ni chikazukanaide
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.40,0:21:02.08,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&H4A2EFB&\blur3}Yasashii koe de
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.08,0:21:06.36,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&H4A2EFB&\blur3}Tada kono mama de itai dake
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.36,0:21:10.67,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&H4A2EFB&\blur3}Yusaburanaide
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.67,0:21:13.84,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&H4A2EFB&\blur3}Na no ni
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.84,0:21:22.96,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Daremo kuzusenai kizukiageta barikeedo
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.96,0:21:35.99,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Kataku tozashiteta hazu datta no ni doushite
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.99,0:21:49.75,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Do you hear weary heart’s S.O.S.?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.37,0:20:31.88,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HFFAE04&\blur3}Foi algo agradável e doce... até que ganhei juízo
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.88,0:20:40.39,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HFFAE04&\blur3}Sempre foi algo cruel, escuro e doloroso
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.39,0:20:45.02,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HACD837&\blur3}Toda vez que eu me aproximo... toda vez que eu brilho
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.02,0:20:49.06,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HACD837&\blur3}meu peito começa a acelerar
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.06,0:20:53.04,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HDB2594&\blur3}Estou feliz, mas dói
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.04,0:20:57.40,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HDB2594&\blur3}De agora em diante, eu não deveria me forçar
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.40,0:21:02.08,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&H4A2EFB&\blur3}Mas diga com uma voz mais suave...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.08,0:21:06.36,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&H4A2EFB&\blur3}Eu só quero ficar assim
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.36,0:21:10.67,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&H4A2EFB&\blur3}Não me force assim...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.67,0:21:13.84,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&H4A2EFB&\blur3}Porém...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.84,0:21:22.96,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Era para ser uma fortaleza que ninguém iria penetrar
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.96,0:21:35.99,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Deveria ser impenetrável, mas por quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.99,0:21:49.75,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Você ouve o chamado de emergência deste coração?
